 suggest challenges for performing model\nselection across long time series. We further anticipate that our findings will\ncontribute to the rapidly growing field of epidemiological forecasting and may\nrelate more broadly to the predictability of complex adaptive systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Mar 2017 17:04:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Mar 2017 12:21:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 28 Mar 2017 17:21:43 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2017 17:11:32 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2018 17:00:39 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2018 14:29:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-11"}
